sequenceDiagram
  participant Genesis
  participant Inception
  participant GIB as GIB Registry
  participant Twin
  participant Search

  Genesis->>Genesis: verify manifest + signatures
  Genesis->>Inception: bringup (bootstrap)
  Inception->>GIB: seed schemas (subjects)
  Inception->>Twin: seed snapshots
  alt connected
    Twin->>Search: publish + replicate
  else disconnected
    Twin->>Twin: queue carriers for later sync
  end
